Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天沒有蛋糕Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有蛋糕我就不來了Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,新來的是打成一片 還是喧賓奪主了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快端蛋糕上來Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕！蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天我睡過頭了 茶倒有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那種東西才不能代替蛋糕Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕Death 蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 小環
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟說好的不一樣Death哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說蛋糕任我吃我才過來的Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再說 我只是路過這裡的路人 被你們誘拐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,%^￥%%￥%^#￥%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 那個…社團的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,學長也被誘拐了Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就跟我一樣是受害者Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一起來絕食抗議Death吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕！蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好萌啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能這樣疼妹妹 真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹真讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是妹妹Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不給蛋糕給我的人滾一邊Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那我讓哥哥做給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 但是蛋糕還是惠做得好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 小環同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音學姐可是三年級的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的學姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這種口氣有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama做錯什麼了Death呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,學長才不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,給我簡單易懂地說明一下Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跟那種事比起來 趕快蛋糕Death 蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠每天都拼命做蛋糕 很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一兩天也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 很辛苦的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每天兩點爬起來做蛋糕的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,兩點爬起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要自己洗澡 頭也要自己梳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瘦了兩公斤 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這方面不用加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生 在等著 被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經輕飄飄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有蛋糕我不會再過來了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 Kyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,用第二形態治治她 別保留啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,給我拽一拽那個傲慢娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什 什麼Death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼Death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要來嗎 要來Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 別太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是俺曼 第二形態！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,超級Kyoron啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama是什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我的名字是環Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(701,650)}Tamaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就叫你狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(718,650)}tanuki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama不喜歡的話 以後就叫你狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(884,650)}tanuki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama就行了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我想吃蛋糕Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,笑嘻嘻笨姐姐…不是 惠學姐親手做的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想做給她吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那週一週二做給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠…惠每天做很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 幹得好 Kyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,值得表揚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,謝 謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama來了以後 感覺零食開銷加倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃那麼多洋芋片 會胖成肥豬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,洋芋片卡路里很高的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,洋芋片的重量中 脂質占了百分之三十五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而脂質則是食品中卡路里最高的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 脂質卻是非常美味的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,人們總是說抵擋不住肥美的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的味覺 在總處於飢餓狀態的原始時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就未曾發生過改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以洋芋片的三分之一是油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 喀滋喀滋地吃洋芋片就相當於咕嚕咕嚕地喝油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吃那麼多洋芋片會變胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,減肥很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,吃那麼多巧克力 不怕胖Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個比較細 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama也沒問題Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,無論吃多少都吃不胖Death
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,超多奶油 給你搞得油水充足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,求之不得Death
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做蛋糕嚐味道的時候 吸收的卡路里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.32,Comment,,0,0,0,,好吃～好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼 脫襪子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 你想我穿上襪子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很滑難度很大的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 很重哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,別騙人啦 才沒那麼重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才三十公斤左右而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說得 也對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼的…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是部長的特技按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她突然說要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為是顛倒的那個什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我在書上看過這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？顛倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 抱歉 能把這事給忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能來踩一踩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對新手來說有點過於著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 請你忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次感受到小不點迷你身材的優越感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐在做按摩啊 還是泰式的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那～我～也～來～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別隨便模仿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠 出人命啦 出人命啦 要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好重 好重 好重！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是蔬菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是 胡蘿蔔 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是 蕪菁 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 綺羅羅 你幹嘛吃蔬菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 問了 居然問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還忍著不問 這個傢伙居然問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼不看狀況的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,KY啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他的情況下反而不會看狀況 我是這麼預測的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是他溫柔的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,AKY嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.12,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：{\u1}AKY{\u0}\N「{\fnDFGMaruGothic-SB}あえて空気読まない{\fn0}」硬是不看狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,硬是不看狀況啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃 蔬菜 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,傑拉說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是小傑拉丁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被罵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個成熟的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃 蔬菜 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃 蔬菜 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,裁決 被告接受梳理之刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 我又幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是哪門子的刑罰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓Kyoron那個傢伙幫你梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是Kyoron幫我梳頭那個時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,當時提議讓惠同學也梳梳看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒錯 沒錯 是說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 請施加梳理的刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個天使般的生物還搞不清狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真央 這只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,惠同學終究會親身體會到這個刑罰的恐怖之處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我也有幾個疑問…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 這是哪門子的刑罰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這個倒可以回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是她在家裡總是虐待我的刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她在虐待你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我自己洗澡 頭髮也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 請你說明一下梳頭怎麼變成刑罰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,駁回 這是少女的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我有沒有選擇權呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 弄疼你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡鉤住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,天使墮入凡間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,惠終於體會到這個刑罰的恐怖之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,梳頭的人被施與梳頭的刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,漢摩拉比法典中也記載了同害報復的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:45.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：漢摩拉比法典最重要的原則是 以牙還牙 以眼還眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真少見啊 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天坐被爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也快要收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正在道別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要收起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 紫 你最近也不怎麼用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 因為 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最近很暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 這個要放到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要邊開電風扇 邊用被爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那都成了忍耐大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯哎 搞起來 在夏天最熱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那還真有GJ部風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,被爐 收起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一切事物 有開始便有終結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,短暫方能精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是前任部長的名言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,前任部長是什麼東西Death呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個生物打娘胎裡居然不是部長Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好痛 好痛Death
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要咬我的話我就以牙還牙Death
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama也漸漸變得GJ部了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,難得一次 大家一起進被爐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 惠 趕緊泡好茶來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,五人的陣型已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在加上Tama有六個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當中除了真央她就是最小了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 讓她坐在誰的膝蓋上不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那小Tama 來我這裡 這裡 這裡Death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,綺羅羅 很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好狡猾 這可是我提議的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～妹妹真讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要亂碰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 Kyoron 你也來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你的椅子鬧哪樣啊 只會摸摸狗頭而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的椅子可附帶梳頭機能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能護理我的秀髮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音姐姐 她看扁我們了Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那我們也來梳梳頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自掘墳墓Death了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～不要解開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 這邊也來梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～～～
